Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=23}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.35,0:00:06.77,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Uau... Um atum gigante elefante, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.77,0:00:09.90,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! Mal posso esperar pra cozinhar!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:03.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah! Isso foi divertido!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.63,0:00:11.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.23,0:00:15.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que foi, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.77,0:00:17.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O ar mudou...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.42,0:00:18.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O ar?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:19.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai chover.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:21.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hein? Com o tempo bonito desse jeito?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:23.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao tem duvida.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:26.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, tem alguem na\Nplataforma de execucao!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:27.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quem diabos e aquele?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:34.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Aquele velho disse que o Rei dos\NPiratas morreu aqui ha vinte e dois anos.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:35.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele apareceu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:40.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Sim! Ficamos vigiando a praca como ordenado,\Ne entao o homem do cartaz de procurado...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:41.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:43.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos com estilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:50.25,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele foi direto ate la...\NAguarde, pirralho.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:01:03.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uau! Entao era isso que o\NRei dos Piratas via...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.39,0:01:05.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por favor, espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:07.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capitao Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.94,0:01:09.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Venha comigo, Tashigi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:06.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei! Voce ai em cima!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:09.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desca agora mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:11.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:15.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa e uma plataforma de execucao especial\Nusada pelo Governo Mundial!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:17.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desca agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:24.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hmph! Agora nao e\Nhora pra peixes pequenos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:25.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:29.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu tava te procurando, Luffy.\NQuanto tempo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:38.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao me diga que voce esqueceu meu rosto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:40.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:42.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela e deslumbrante!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:43.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela e uma mulher de beleza incomparavel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:46.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A pele dela parece tao macia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:49.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao conheco ninguem como voce.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:51.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quem diabos e voce?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:53.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nunca vou te esquecer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:57.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,porque voce e o primeiro homem\Nque ja me bateu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:59.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que? {\i1}Eu{\i0} te bati?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:05.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quando seu punho apaixonado me acertou...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:10.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, foi tao bom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:20.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Rapazes... Nestes mares,\Nquem e a mais bela de todas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:23.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Voce, e claro!\N– Voce, e claro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo. Sou eu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:30.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao existe um homem neste mundo\Nque nao se curve diante da minha beleza.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:33.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E eu adoro um homem forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:37.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou fazer voce ser meu, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:38.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:40.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,De jeito nenhum! Quem diabos e voce?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ainda nao descobriu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:46.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aqui e a policia! Venha quieta, moca!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:50.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce esta presa por\Nagredir nosso capitao da policia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:54.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E {\i1}voce{\i0}! Desca da\Nplataforma de execucao!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:57.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh? Quem voce disse que ia prender?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:05:00.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tenente, temos\Num problema! Ela e linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.39,0:05:02.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Dane-se a beleza! Prende ela!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:05.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Ela e tao linda\Nque ofusca a vista!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:07.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que bom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:10.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estamos sendo bombardeados!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:11.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela vai ser atingida!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:16.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,M-Mas o que...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A fonte deslizou e passou direto...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:20.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que acabou de acontecer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:26.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso foi perigoso, sabia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:32.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Desculpa com estilo. Mas sua pele macia\Nesta ilesa, claro. Entao sem danos...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:35.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,belissima Alvida!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:37.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hein? Alvida?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:42.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao vejo a Alvida.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:45.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sou a Alvida, seu idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:48.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Serio? Voce nao parece nada com ela...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.09,0:05:53.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu mudei depois de comer uma fruta do diabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:56.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O nome da fruta e...\Na Fruta Lisa-Lisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:06:02.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Todos os ataques deslizam na minha pele\Ne me deixam ilesa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:07.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Infelizmente, minha beleza\Nnao podia melhorar muito mais.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:12.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas teve uma grande mudanca.\NAh, sim, minhas sardas sumiram.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:14.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,N-Nao, nao era bem isso que eu quis dizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:16.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Depois de me tornar uma nova pessoa,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:20.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu me aliei a alguem\Nporque ele tambem queria te encontrar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:33.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora, a estrela principal pode\Nfazer sua entrada com estilo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:38.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desde o dia que voce me mandou voando,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,eu fiquei obcecado\Nem me vingar de voce.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:44.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So isso me levou a\Nfinalmente encontrar minha tripulacao.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:48.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Foi realmente uma grande aventura.\NEu estava sem partes do meu corpo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:51.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu ri, passei por um inferno\Ne fiz novos amigos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:53.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu chamo de "A Grande Aventura do Pequeno Buggy."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:55.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sabe, o Buggy era...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.73,0:06:57.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que eu to contando {\i1}pra voce{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:07:00.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que? Espera, qual\Nera seu nome mesmo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:03.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bogey... Nao, Boogie.\NTalvez fosse Behee...? Ou nao...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:04.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, lembrei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bufao!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:12.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bufao?! Para de brincadeira!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:15.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce continua irritante como sempre, seu idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:17.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Esse e o Buggy, o Palhaco!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:18.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sao p-piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:23.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sao os Piratas do Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:28.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pessoal! Fiquem estilosos onde estao!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:34.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou mostrar pra todos voces\No quao assustador eu sou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah! E o Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:39.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So agora voce lembrou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O-O que ta acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:49.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quanto tempo, homem de borracha.\NComo vai o Roronoa Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:52.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Certo, Cabaji. Bom trabalho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:08:00.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Eu peco que meus centenas de bilhoes de\Nseguidores ao redor do mundo observem bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:03.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estamos prestes a realizar uma\Nexecucao publica super estilosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:09.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy! Voce nao\Nconsegue mexer nem um centimetro agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce deveria se sentir honrado, Chapeu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:15.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce vai morrer no mesmo lugar\Nque o Rei dos Piratas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:30.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A pressao atmosferica\Nesta caindo loucamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:32.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nunca vi uma\Nqueda tao bizarra assim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:35.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora que voce falou,\No vento esta diferente mesmo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:38.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma tempestade vai atingir essa ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.61,0:08:40.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,U-Uma tempestade?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:43.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E melhor voltarmos logo pro\Nnavio ou vamos ter problemas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:44.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai ser forte?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:45.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:45.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:48.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce viu ele?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce quer dizer o Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:54.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Tem piratas aqui!\N– Tem piratas aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:56.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tem piratas aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:57.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Corre!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:59.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E o Buggy, o Palhaco!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:00.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que eles disseram?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:01.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Buggy, o Palhaco!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:09.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que? Entao...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:10.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,S-Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:15.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Alem do Chapeu de Palha Luffy,\NBuggy, o Palhaco e Alvida, a Clava de Ferro,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:20.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,ambos sendo piratas notorios do East Blue,\Nchegaram pra tomar a praca!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:23.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bem debaixo do meu nariz...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:26.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que escoria arrogante.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:29.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que devemos fazer, Capitao Smoker?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:32.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A unidade um vai se posicionar no mar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:35.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A unidade dois vai cercar\Na praca secretamente pelas ruas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:38.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O restante ficara de prontidao\Nno alcance de tiro da praca.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:39.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E so isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:40.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:43.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Passe esta ordem pra unidade um.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:43.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim, senhor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:47.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,"Destruam qualquer navio pirata\Nassim que avistarem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:53.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao deixem nenhum pirata sair\Ndessa ilha. Nenhum sequer."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:00.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma execucao!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:01.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma execucao vai comecar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:04.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Buggy, o Palhaco, vai\Nexecutar o Chapeu de Palha Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O Luffy vai ser executado?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:08.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aquele idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:09.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:10.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cuida disso!
Comment: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:13.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ahh... Ahh... Ahhhhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:14.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,S-S-S-Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:17.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Trata isso como uma dama! Entendeu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:17.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ops!
Comment: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:19.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ahhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:19.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A gente tambem precisa correr!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:21.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei! Ei, N-N-Nami! Pra onde a gente ta indo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:23.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pro porto, claro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:26.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O-O porto? Ah, faz sentido!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capitao Smoker! Por favor, de uma olhada.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:32.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,As coisas estao ficando estranhas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:33.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:35.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que...! A-Aquele garoto...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:38.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que ele ta fazendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:44.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy. Nao pode ser!\NParece que ele vai ser morto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:46.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capitao, vamos\Nintervir agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:47.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Idiota. Nao seja apressado.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:51.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um pirata ta prestes a matar outro pirata.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:53.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Otimo. Eles estao nos\Npoupando o trabalho.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:57.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Escutem! Quando a cabeca do Chapeu de Palha rolar,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:01.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,cerquem o Buggy, a Alvida\Ne todos que estao com eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:02.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao deem tempo pra eles pensarem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:13.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O pirata Monkey D. Luffy e um criminoso\Ne sera executado com estilo por...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:15.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,me irritar com a atitude dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:20.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aproveitem com estilo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:25.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E a primeira vez que\Neu vejo uma execucao.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:28.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quem ta sendo executado e {\i1}voce{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:29.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que?! Para de brincadeira!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:33.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Voce{\i0} que pare de brincadeira!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:36.09,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tira essa tabua! Seu desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:40.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E agora, a execucao publica\Nvai comecar com estilo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:40.35,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tira isso! Voce me enganou!\NSeu idiota! Seu desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:45.35,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ahhh!! Para com isso! Ahhh!\NEu nao quero morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:48.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tem uma grande nuvem cumulus\Nno ceu a leste!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:53.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma tempestade esta vindo.\NVai ser inimaginavelmente forte...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:58.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se o Buggy, o Luffy e os outros\Nenlouquecerem, a Marinha vai agir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:02.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estamos perdidos se o navio for levado\Npro alto mar quando tivermos que fugir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:03.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E, isso e urgente!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:07.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A Marinha pode ja\Nter comecado a agir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:10.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O {\i1}Going Merry{\i0} esta em perigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.63,0:12:14.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O-O {\i1}Going Merry{\i0}\Nvai cair nas maos da Marinha?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:18.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos, Nami! R-Rapido!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:20.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Espera por mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:23.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Rapido pro porto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.02,0:12:28.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\b1\bord1.5\shad1.2\fnFOT-Greco Std B Strp\fs33}♪ Andando na Richie Bike! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:33.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\b1\bord1.5\shad1.2\fnFOT-Greco Std B Strp\fs33}♪ Quem e esse homem?\NQuem? Quem? Quem e esse homem?! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:36.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\b1\bord1.5\shad1.2\fnFOT-Greco Std B Strp\fs33}♪ Eu! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:39.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entao esse e o navio do cara de borracha...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:45.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E maior que o primeiro,\Ncomo se ele fosse um pirata de verdade...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:49.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ta na hora dele ser executado\Ncom estilo pelo Capitao Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:57.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Porem...! So por precaucao, caso o cara de borracha,\Nque nao tem chance de escapar,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:58.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,acabe escapando...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:01.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\b1\bord1.5\shad1.2\fnFOT-Greco Std B Strp\fs33}♪ E nosso dever queimar esse navio! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:10.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desculpa. Eu nao faco mais.\NPor favor, me solta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:11.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que eu faria isso, idiota?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:15.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hmph! Isso e o que acontece\Nquando alguem vai contra a gente.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:19.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Acho que e o fim do homem\Nque eu estava de olho...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:22.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ja que voce tem uma grande plateia,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:25.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,quer dizer alguma coisa\Nantes de morrer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:28.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao? Bom, tudo bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:34.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao faria diferenca mesmo\Nja que voce vai morrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:40.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sou o homem que vai ser\No Rei dos Piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:49.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:52.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Ele acabou de dizer\N"Rei dos Piratas"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:54.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Logo nessa cidade...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:57.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que loucura de se dizer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:14:00.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bem, entao acho que e isso...\Nseu pirralho de borracha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:06.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Parem...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:06.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O-O que?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:07.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– ...a execucao!\N– ...a execucao!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:08.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:14.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Zoro! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.46,0:14:19.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E o Cacador de Piratas Z-Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:20.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:26.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, ai esta voce, Zoro!\NMas voce chegou um pouco tarde demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:29.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Vamos derrubar...\N– ...aquela plataforma de execucao!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:32.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Roronoa Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:36.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pessoal... peguem eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Deixa com a gente!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:40.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Irmanzinha Alvida!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:45.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Saiam do caminho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:57.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nem o Zoro pode me parar agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:15:01.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esse e o fim do seu capitao!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:03.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Maldito desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:09.51,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Se eu pudesse derrubar a plataforma...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:11.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Escutem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:14.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}No instante que a cabeca do Monkey D. Luffy cair,\Nvamos atacar todos de uma vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:19.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Todas as unidades. Preparem-se para batalha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:20.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Sim, senhor!\N– Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:24.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zoro! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:26.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Usopp! Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:25.31,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Anda logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:26.52,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Isso e pesado!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:28.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desculpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:30.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu... morri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:31.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eu... morri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:34.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Idiota...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:37.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao diz uma besteira dessas!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:38.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele sorriu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:29.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu ainda to vivo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:31.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:39.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Ei, voce acredita em Deus?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:39.39,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ufa, que sorte a minha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:42.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Para de falar besteira.\NVamos sair logo dessa cidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:41.89,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eu fiquei preocupado por um momento.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:45.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E uma coisa atras da outra.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:52.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora! Encurralem os piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:55.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Sim!\N– Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:16:57.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,La vem eles!
Comment: 0,0:16:57.33,0:16:57.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Tsk! - OG}Tch!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:08.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Incrivel! Incrivel!\NDe repente ficou uma loucura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:10.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Incrivel! Ahh! Incrivel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:11.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:13.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ahhh... Z-Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:15.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sei que isso e empolgante,\Nmas a gente precisa ir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:20.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E melhor a gente voltar logo pro navio ou\Nnunca vamos conseguir sair da ilha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:22.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao vamos conseguir\Nentrar na Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:24.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que?! Isso nao e bom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:27.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Os Chapeus de Palha estao fugindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:29.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capturem eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:30.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vao atras deles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:36.99,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que ele sorriu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.15,0:17:40.47,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele sabia que seria salvo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:47.37,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao. Naquele momento, ele genuinamente\Nachou que sua vida tinha acabado.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:52.13,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele estava preparado\Npra aceitar a morte e sorriu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:54.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capitao, temos que\Nprender os piratas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:18:00.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei... voce ja viu um pirata que\Nsorriu na plataforma de execucao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:05.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,N-Nunca! Mesmo se estiverem bancando os duroes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:09.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,na hora da morte,\Ntodos ficam palidos e morrem em desespero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:12.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aquele homem de chapeu de palha sorriu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:20.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,assim como o Rei dos Piratas, vinte e dois anos atras nessa cidade...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:23.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger sorriu na\Nplataforma de execucao.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:33.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capitao...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.95,0:18:36.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra onde foi o Chapeu de Palha?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:40.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele correu em direcao ao mar, senhor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:45.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que a unidade um ta fazendo? Ja deviam\Nter destruido o navio deles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:49.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bom... Eles tiveram que voltar pra\Nreabastecer porque nao conseguiram
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:52.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,acender a polvora\Npor causa da chuva repentina...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:53.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:58.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma unidade reserva esta se\Nmovendo pra atacar o navio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:19:03.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capitao Smoker! Se deixarmos eles zarparem\Nagora, vao entrar na Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:09.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O vento esta soprando pro oeste... O navio deles tera vento a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.37,0:19:13.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sao tudo coincidencias?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:19.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E como se os ceus tivessem\Nplanos pra aquele jovem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:23.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E melhor a gente se apressar\Nou vamos ter problemas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:25.06,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Vamos conseguir chegar\Nna Grand Line assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:26.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sou Smoker, o Cao Branco.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:31.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Pela minha honra como capitao do Quartel-General\Nda Marinha, eu nao vou deixar aquele homem sair dessa ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:39.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que tempestade e essa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:42.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se nao sairmos logo,\Nvamos ficar presos aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:45.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A Nami tem razao que devemos\Nvoltar logo pro navio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:50.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Me atacar e perda de tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:55.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao existe homem vivo\Nque consiga tocar minha pele lisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:01.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu acabei de ver um campo de flores...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.46,0:20:03.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capitao Buggy, voce ta vivo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:04.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,De jeito nenhum eu ia morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:06.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Buggy, isso nao ta bom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:08.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Os Marinheiros do QG\Nnao vao desistir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:11.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hmph. Como se eu me importasse\Npra onde a Marinha mete o nariz...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:13.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,De quem voce disse\Nque o nariz ta aparecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao disse nada disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:19.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Qual e o plano?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:22.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu! Vai atras do Gomu Gomu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:25.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O Mohji e o Richie ja devem\Nter queimado o navio dele.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.27,0:20:27.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele nao pode sair dessa ilha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:30.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos acabar com ele\Ne sair dessa ilha, galera!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:31.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Sim!\N– Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:32.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Motor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:34.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Sim, Capitao!\N– Sim, Capitao!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:36.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Bara Bara Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:37.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,La vamos nos!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:39.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ligando o motor de bombas!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Preparem a rampa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:46.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Sim, Irmanzinha Alvida!\N– Sim, Irmanzinha Alvida!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:47.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Sem Atrito...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:52.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Trilhos Lisa-Lisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:00.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao deixem os piratas escaparem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:08.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O... O que e essa fumaca?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:13.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que droga...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:15.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}White Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:21.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.79,0:21:25.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao tenho tempo pra peixes pequenos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.02,0:21:27.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Ele e forte demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:29.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O poder da Fruta\Nda Fumaca-Fumaca...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.19,0:21:31.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele derrubou a tripulacao do Buggy\Nnum piscar de olhos...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.37,0:21:34.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:43.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capitao! Ele pegou\Ntodos nos de uma vez so!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:45.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como se atreve, Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:49.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que e essa rede de aco irritante?!\NAtirando uma pistola estranha dessas...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:53.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}A Marinha desenvolveu esse tiro de gaiola\Ncomo forma de lidar com poderes de fruta do diabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:54.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:21:59.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tragam minha Billower Bike!\NEu vou atras do Chapeu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:00.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.61,0:22:04.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.22,0:22:10.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Por que essa chuva repentina,\Njusto quando a gente precisa queimar esse navio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:16.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga! Isso ta ruim, Richie!\NA gente nao consegue fazer fogo assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.03,0:22:17.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mais uma vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.17,0:22:23.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Paciencia, Richie! Eu te alimento depois.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:27.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que voce ta fazendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:29.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mohji!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.69,0:22:32.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, se nao e a ladrazinha.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.71,0:22:36.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:44.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Estrela Letal de Ovo Podre!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.35,0:22:52.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:54.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga! A chuva fez minha mao escorregar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.09,0:23:01.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Richie! So uma vez, da pra nao...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:03.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora! Vamos subir no navio!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:04.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:07.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Para ai! Voces tem que passar por mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:10.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sou Mohji, imediato da\Ntripulacao pirata do Buggy, o Palhaco!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.86,0:23:13.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao vou deixar voces colocarem\Nnem um pe nesse nav–
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:17.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Preparem pra atirar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:19.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A Marinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:20.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso ta ruim!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.77,0:23:21.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mirem!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.91,0:23:25.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.89,0:23:33.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Contatem a unidade de canhoes!\NVamos capturar o navio pirata!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.17,0:23:33.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:35.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,N-N-N-Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.03,0:23:36.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.91,0:23:49.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Em que direcao fica o mar?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.65,0:23:53.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao consigo saber pra onde estamos indo\Npor causa dessa chuva toda!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.11,0:23:54.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,La estao eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.33,0:23:59.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Malditos persistentes!\NDevemos parar e lutar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.25,0:24:00.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao temos tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:02.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.50,0:24:04.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quem e aquela mulher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.26,0:24:06.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.89,0:24:10.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao sabia que voce era\No Roronoa Zoro, e ainda por cima um pirata.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.87,0:24:12.88,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce vai tomar {\i0}essa{\i1} espada tambem?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.55,0:24:18.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce... Voce mentiu pra mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.51,0:24:22.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que?! O que voce fez pra ela?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.02,0:24:24.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce nunca perguntou meu nome, so isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.04,0:24:26.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nunca menti pra voce.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.79,0:24:32.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Viloes como voce nao podem\Nser permitidos a carregar uma espada tao renomada!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.49,0:24:35.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu reivindico a lamina lendaria\NWado Ichimonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.73,0:24:47.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Seu filho da mae!\NComo se atreve a atacar uma dama!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.75,0:24:49.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai na frente.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.39,0:24:51.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.31,0:24:57.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, Zoro! Se voce machucar\Na moca, eu nao te perdoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.51,0:24:58.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sargento Tashigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.37,0:25:19.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa e uma espada\Nque voce nao vai conseguir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.45,0:25:22.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A Sargento Tashigi perdeu...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.39,0:25:24.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas ela e {\i1}a{\i0} Sargento Tashigi...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.87,0:25:28.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ate logo. Eu to com pressa, entao...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.75,0:25:34.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que nao me da o golpe final?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.23,0:25:37.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E porque eu sou mulher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.03,0:25:42.67,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce tem sorte, Zoro.\NVoce nasceu menino.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.01,0:25:46.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Homens podem ser fisicamente\Nmais fortes que mulheres,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.33,0:25:49.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,mas e tao humilhante que\Nvoce nao lute a serio!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.62,0:25:54.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce nao tem como entender o que e\Ndesejar ter nascido menino!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.67,0:25:57.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao carrego uma espada como acessorio!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.11,0:26:01.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao suporto saber que voce existe!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.91,0:26:05.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou te contar! E o seu rosto!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.84,0:26:08.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce e identica a uma boa\Namiga minha que morreu ha muito tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.77,0:26:12.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E agora voce ta dizendo\Na mesma coisa que ela dizia!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.07,0:26:14.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quem e voce pra imitar\Nela, sua imitadora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.38,0:26:17.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que droga...?! Amadureca\Ne pense antes de falar!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.05,0:26:18.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sou quem eu sou!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.89,0:26:22.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao sei como era sua amiga,\Nmas quem ta chateada aqui sou eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.89,0:26:24.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Talvez {\i1}ela{\i0} e que seja a imitadora!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.05,0:26:28.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O-O que voce disse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.34,0:26:31.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vejo a saida! O porto e logo ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.86,0:26:39.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, quem e agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.21,0:26:43.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce finalmente chegou...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.69,0:26:46.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Chapeu de Palha Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.93,0:27:02.77,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Vontades herdadas...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.77,0:27:05.51,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,as mares do tempo\Ne os sonhos da humanidade...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.51,0:27:08.68,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Eles nao podem ser parados.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.68,0:27:11.73,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Enquanto as pessoas buscarem liberdade,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.73,0:27:14.48,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,essas coisas jamais deixarao de existir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.53,0:27:18.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um pirata, hein? Por mim tudo bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.91,0:27:30.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sou o Capitao Smoker.\NEu comando Loguetown pela Marinha.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.61,0:27:32.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce esta preso.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.50,0:27:35.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hein? Preso? Esquece!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.92,0:27:39.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu to indo pra Grand Line\Npra me tornar o Rei dos Piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.61,0:27:40.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Rei dos Piratas?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.05,0:27:43.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu me recuso a ser preso\Nnum lugar como esse!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.82,0:27:46.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entao voce vai ter que me derrotar primeiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.59,0:27:48.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.87,0:27:52.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sanji, vai na frente. Eu ja vou.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.65,0:28:00.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.12,0:28:07.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Disparem os canhoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.77,0:28:26.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se ficarmos aqui mais tempo,\No {\i1}Going Merry{\i0} vai ser afundado!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.64,0:28:35.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,V-Voces vao zarpar?\NO Luffy e os outros ainda nao voltaram!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.55,0:28:38.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao temos escolha!\NE melhor do que ser afundados!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.75,0:28:41.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Leme todo pra direita!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.86,0:28:46.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E o grupo do Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.62,0:28:48.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A gente pega eles depois!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.41,0:28:50.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao deixem eles escaparem! Sigam eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.79,0:28:51.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.64,0:28:53.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.91,0:28:54.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.80,0:28:57.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami, voltei!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.38,0:28:59.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Onde estao o Luffy e o Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.76,0:29:02.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sera que a gente consegue\Npegar aqueles malditos idiotas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.51,0:29:05.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.45,0:29:06.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Atras de voce!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.71,0:29:14.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga, nao tem fim!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.64,0:29:16.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu dou cobertura! Me leva mais perto!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.43,0:29:20.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao da! Tem uma corrente forte\Nnos afastando da costa!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.09,0:29:21.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, dane-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.10,0:29:22.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.94,0:29:24.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desgraçados!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.79,0:29:35.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usopp! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.33,0:29:47.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que?! O que?! O que ta acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.22,0:29:56.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu comi a Fruta da Fumaca-Fumaca,\Nentao meu corpo vira fumaca quando eu quero!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.59,0:30:17.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que foi? Ja cansou?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.76,0:30:29.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.59,0:30:42.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que? Eca, que nojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.01,0:30:48.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}White Blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.16,0:30:51.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Seu desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.94,0:30:55.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.15,0:31:00.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entendeu agora? Voce nao\Nconsegue entrar na Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.25,0:31:02.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E isso que eu to te dizendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.17,0:31:11.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce e procurado por trinta milhoes de belly?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.39,0:31:14.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Parece que sua sorte do diabo\Nacabou.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.69,0:31:19.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao tenha tanta certeza.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.80,0:31:21.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce e...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.81,0:31:36.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O-O que ta acontecendo? Quem e? Quem ta ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.29,0:31:40.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O governo quer a sua cabeca.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.11,0:31:45.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O mundo esta esperando nossa resposta.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.59,0:32:22.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I-Isso e...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.89,0:32:27.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O-O que acabou de acontecer?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.97,0:32:32.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.31,0:32:34.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.34,0:32:35.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.83,0:32:38.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E melhor a gente se apressar antes\Nque o navio seja levado!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.43,0:32:39.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.85,0:32:42.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.73,0:32:46.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.38,0:32:47.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.63,0:32:49.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu tenho um mau pressentimento...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.20,0:32:52.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.12,0:32:52.53,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Ahhh, eu sabia!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.71,0:33:03.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pessoal...!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.17,0:33:12.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Serio, aquela rajada estilosa\Nfoi um golpe de sorte.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.00,0:33:15.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa fuga so foi possivel porque\Neu sempre mantenho a calma.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.97,0:33:17.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra onde agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.50,0:33:24.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos direto pra\NGrand Line. Que nostalgico!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.15,0:33:41.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se essa e sua decisao, entao va!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.49,0:33:45.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que?! Por que voce ajudou aquele homem...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.63,0:33:46.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.43,0:33:54.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que razao haveria pra\Ninterferir na partida de um homem?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.37,0:34:08.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Zarpar! Vamos atras do Chapeu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.27,0:34:09.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.37,0:34:12.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos entrar na Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.73,0:34:16.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,M-Mas, Capitao!\NEssa ilha e seu posto.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.37,0:34:18.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que os superiores vao dizer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.35,0:34:22.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Diga a eles que eu disse:\N"Nao me deem ordens!"
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.35,0:34:24.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou junto!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.75,0:34:26.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sargento Tashigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.65,0:34:29.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao posso deixar o Roronoa escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.54,0:34:32.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou captura-lo sem falta!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.55,0:34:35.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uau! Parece que o navio\Nvai virar!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.33,0:34:40.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ve aquela luz?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.89,0:34:42.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O farol da ilha?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.37,0:34:43.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E uma "luz guia."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.81,0:34:46.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A entrada da Grand Line\Nfica logo alem daquela luz.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.85,0:34:49.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A Grand Line fica alem daquela luz...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.59,0:34:50.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que voce quer fazer?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.81,0:34:54.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,P-Precisamos entrar\Ndurante uma tempestade dessas?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.62,0:35:11.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Certo, entao! Que tal fazermos uma\Ncerimonia de lancamento nesse grande mar?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.01,0:35:11.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.96,0:35:12.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah! Boa ideia!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.86,0:35:14.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos la!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.19,0:35:18.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra encontrar o All Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.03,0:35:21.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra ser o Rei dos Piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.45,0:35:24.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra me tornar o maior espadachim!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.99,0:35:29.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra desenhar o mapa do mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.06,0:35:35.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}P-Pra me tornar um bravo guerreiro do mar!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.45,0:35:51.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estamos indo... pra Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.00,0:35:54.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Sim!\N– Sim!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=24}===============================DIALOGUE============================
